<p>Hi <%= @resource.first_name %>!</p>

<p>To change your password, please click on the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token, subdomain: ENV["DEFAULT_SUBDOMAIN"]) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
